<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>Geração Sônica - Rádio Web</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #0a1a2e 100%);
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 16px;
        }

        .radio-card {
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(10, 20, 30, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-radius: 48px;
            padding: 24px 20px 32px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ff00cc, 0 0 5px #00aaff;
        }

        .sub {
            color: #bbb;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .visual {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 25%, #ff44cc, #2266ff);
            border-radius: 35px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 25px black;
        }

        .visual span {
            font-size: 4rem;
            filter: drop-shadow(2px 4px 8px black);
        }

        .player-area {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            border-radius: 60px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        audio {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 40px;
            outline: none;
        }

        .now-playing {
            color: #ffcc88;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        .playlist {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            border-radius: 28px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .playlist h3 {
            color: #ffcc88;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff44cc;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .track {
            padding: 10px 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            color: #ddd;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .track-name {
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .track-time {
            color: #88aaff;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: #5588aa;
        }

        button {
            background: #ff44aa;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="radio-card">
        <h1>⚡ GERAÇÃO SÔNICA</h1>
        <div class="sub">Sua rádio vibrante</div>

        <div class="visual">
            <span>🎧🔊</span>
        </div>

        <div class="player-area">
            <audio controls autoplay>
                <source src="https://www.soundhelix.com/examples/mp3/SoundHelix-Song-1.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
                Seu navegador não suporta áudio.
            </audio>
            <div class="now-playing">🎶 TOCANDO AGORA: Batida Sônica</div>
        </div>

        <div class="playlist">
            <h3>📻 PRÓXIMAS MISSÕES</h3>
            <div class="track"><span class="track-name">🌀 Onda Subterrânea</span><span class="track-time">03:22</span></div>
            <div class="track"><span class="track-name">⚡ Pulso Eletrônico</span><span class="track-time">04:15</span></div>
            <div class="track"><span class="track-name">🎤 Rimas Sônicas</span><span class="track-time">03:45</span></div>
            <div class="track"><span class="track-name">🌌 Nebulosa Synth</span><span class="track-time">05:10</span></div>
        </div>

        <button onclick="alert('⚡ GERAÇÃO SÔNICA - Mais músicas em breve!')">📡 PEDIR MÚSICA</button>

        <footer>
            Rádio Geração Sônica • 24h direto no seu celular
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>.html